---
import PageHeading from "../components/page-heading.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/main.astro";
---

<Layout title="DMCA - Bangla Web Fonts">
  <section class="relative z-20 max-w-3xl mx-auto my-12 px-7 lg:px-0">
    <PageHeading
      title="DMCA"
      description="Last updated: 19 April 2025"
    />




<p class="mt-4">
  <strong>Bangla Web Fonts</strong> hosts fonts and icons that are licensed for public use, redistribution, and embedding. We carefully review the license terms before publishing any assets.
</p>

<p class="mt-6">
  Most of the <strong>fonts</strong> available on this site are licensed under:
</p>

<ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-1 space-y-1">
  <li><span class="font-medium">SIL Open Font License (OFL)</span></li>
  <li><span class="font-medium">GNU GPL with the Font Exception</span></li>
  <li><span class="font-medium">Custom open licenses</span> from the original font creators, often labeled as <span class="italic">"উন্মুক্ত"</span> (open) in the font metadata or official release pages</li>
</ul>

<p class="mt-6">
  Most of the <strong>icons</strong> are sourced under widely used open licenses, such as:
</p>

<ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-1 space-y-1">
  <li><span class="font-medium">Creative Commons</span> (various versions)</li>
  <li><span class="font-medium">MIT License</span></li>
  <li><span class="font-medium">Public Domain</span></li>
  <li><span class="font-medium">SIL Open Font License</span> (for icons generated with font glyphs)</li>
  <li><span class="font-medium">Other permissive open licenses</span> as provided by the original creators</li>
</ul>

<p class="mt-6">
  We carefully verify license information from the original creators’ official websites, metadata, and repositories before including any font, icon or asset on this site.
</p>

<p class="mt-6">
  If you believe a font, icon or any other asset has been included in error or that it infringes your copyright, please contact us at: 
  <a href="mailto:contact.shihab1246@gmail.com" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">contact.shihab1246@gmail.com</a>
</p>




    

  </section>
</Layout>